vable collapse is worth much more, and resilient foods (ALLFED) can overtake AI safety. The opposite of collapse_teaches_better_future. Requires the undiscounted far future. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 6 no_discounting_future_humans → 7 animals_matter_a_lot → 8 suffering_focused → 13 collapse_degrades_future" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJylWGtT4zgW%2FSu3qJ3dpBeC7bzDMlV0E2a6Fnq6gN6pqaYrrdhKosGxvJJNyPYwv32PZDtxSCjcky9UkKVzz33qXn07CPiEpWHyTgb8YHBwfEynp6d0q5iIKJHkK%2Fa%2FJX4sIrpLPcdt0UKqMHgQfEELd%2BSN2qPOqDvqjdwm1XQiY3KbdQNxFwHqTOt0HidCRuTPgDggh2KmpD8TLDSAbt8jlyZMjdiCLUezdM4iXXzwiEVizkI90nLOFzOWFF%2FaNEmTVPH8wGjOkoSr0UIks1EgtC%2FTKBHRtNjeoUiW10cbp4td3ZW4HI6NQrkS2SOdTiZc2ePSTzUPVgo0yZdhyGLNRwGfKhZwnYuwVhgyf0ZsbQqhidHHZTLD74kIOcHU68%2F6mBKjKgsCfUiKwz8i4pqksmCKH8GCbM7BUGisJzOeGfcfGlaJfItxAkbzWGpjhNUGnI0CDkQsCW3RdMKigIUy4jRHAIQN%2Brry7%2FDhq6FqjvPHmPsJDj6wMOUkJxZhHQoNC%2FaW64TG6ZJSI8Yc1Lys2IDOLi8vhufZ7p%2BGH4bXZ7fDcxovacojrljCG%2FGyiDMeiGTDLG%2Fw8RCeTDLhxnJAslifIp%2BrxKg4lwqRtbKQzvZm6rM4DgXXDbpZzhuhnEZSwd21b3H7kOJ%2B%2B6lusax3%2Bs4P9O79id055gnLVmMlx2wsQpGAyFgaNQOTJJ%2BdQ3K%2FNOiC%2BYmETJY7XmBDbGweJYekJXETCFJN4anh58X52eVvx3%2F7QmMeygVywJy1HuWP%2BB0ucRzYsKLFguwg9ZPM9vAWR%2BRC%2FUkoU5yawdHneYDT6baCSLyG07Nqmp%2B9pzqRDSZgQocFF9MZsJGmijObOjNYy8SdptqtnDMt7k%2FoP1DIfPMcz4GxVgnxUQlQT5a7JbsNNxfcabRzwfwxUawklj3AfwYaOvMIYbPCfll8lmElrV0LHWPxKBFzTv8knyVMJ0rGsJjJ6ShlNgNN4jF1lCHkQV27ZnPNl8c3CJuI%2FnR%2BOF4qetD0QapgxlJNf7qNtlk8gaBTxCEVFQVcivy%2FsIhXqKfCxJrabREvt0fbyc2xRQZeXpmEwRjqQTywMUpFIQgI8I2YC50IH35UWEcBthtNCCKxpxESqj6gH2F%2BRqH073lwhDRA1sLANnfz9DkXCulNHCb3rTtKgRor1ES1RJRGKES%2BwO9Deju8%2BOV6mCWbRcg8CbYQZTJljoIdJUcopP4M8bXSn24%2BXV2dXf%2BWhTGqXCYEZEDOIo1lwn2qmfimsw%2FnsIcSDOmdZUW9Qbfw5SSFtlnGHI2XR9kvQtGBlayDsxqSUcOlkCmUbbM6yQceWVSUP2RmqvAzrzuheEAOmtsPgkIRFcT0f1MxnYb82DLUx%2F8SwY%2BNYjGrnjbJUbVQLEz1guKA%2BeXDkOKQZbLyEs4CU%2FQ4PLxcF1EUewaZpnBCdxFBtkVAEch2ZhUaeSfT%2BN%2FCWDY6Z%2BHyI1