unting_future_humans + animals_matter_a_lot + suffering_focused + collapse_degrades_future + time_of_perils_exit&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Time-of-perils optimism: hazard is high during the AI / nuclear transition but collapses once decorrelated, self-sufficient settlements exist — no single catastrophe reaches them all. The window closes, the expected future stretches far past the background-hazard baseline, and x-risk reduction during the window is what unlocks it (Ord, The Precipice; the multiplanetary-backup argument). Mutually exclusive with the view that early expansion re-arms the hazard. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 6 no_discounting_future_humans → 7 animals_matter_a_lot → 8 suffering_focused → 13 collapse_degrades_future → 14 time_of_perils_exit" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJylWWtz2zYW%2FSt3PNtdKWvLpN6y151xYrnN1HmM7WynE2cUiIQkrCmCC5CW1dT97T0ASImK5AlTffHQIHDuuU%2FcS305CPmEZVH6Sob84OTg%2BJjOzs7oVjERUyopUOz3JR4WMd1lTc9v00KqKHwQfEELf9QcdUbdUW%2FUH%2FmtEV7WdCoT8tt1g3IXA%2B1c62yepELGFMwAekIeJUzJYCZYZDD9QZN8mjA1Ygu2HM2yOYt18aJJLBZzFumRlnO%2BmLG0eNOhSZZmiucHRnOWplyNFiKdjUKhA5nFqYinxfYuxbK8Pto4XezqrcTlcGwUyZXIPulsMuHKHpdBpnm4UqBFgYwilmg%2BCvlUsZDrXMRqS5tSMecjORklwIAM%2FihSa6MhC2bE1oYSmhi9X6YzPE9ExAm%2BWL%2FWx5QaQ7Aw1IekOBwoYq5JKgum%2BBHsy%2BYc%2FIXGejrjzvT%2F0rBZHFiMU%2FCdJ1IbE6024GwcciBiSWiLplMWhyySMac5IiRq0OdVAAwfPhuq5jh%2FTHiQ4uADizJOcmIR1rHSsGAvuU5pnC0pM2LMQc3Lip3Q%2BdXV5fDC7f5p%2BHZ4fX47vKDxkqY85oqlvJEsi0DkoUg3zPICLw%2Fh59QJN5YDksX6EAdcpUbFuVSIu5WFtNvr1GdJEgmuG3SznDciOY2lQjDUviSdQ0oGnae6xbLeGXg%2F0KvXp3bnmKfMrSZKjtlYRCIFkbE0aoYmiz56h%2BR%2FatAlC1IJmUxxB4UNibF5nB6SlsRNIEg1haeGHxcX51e%2FHf%2FjE415JBfIEHPWepQ%2F4jla4jiwYUWLBdlhFqTO9vAWR1xD%2FUkkM5yawdEXefjT2baCSMuG17dqmsf%2BU53IBhMwocOCi%2BkM2EhixZlNrBmsZeJOU%2B1WzpkW96f0Xyhk3jW9pgdjrdLlvRKgni53S%2FYbfi642%2BjkgvljqlhJLHuA%2Fww0dOYxwmaF%2Fbx4l38lrX0LnWDxyKQi%2FZsCljKdKpnAYibj44zZDDSJx9RRnsEuqGvXbK758vgGYRP