ical-stakes move it pushes back on. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 6 no_discounting_future_humans → 7 animals_matter_a_lot → 8 suffering_focused → 13 collapse_degrades_future → 14 time_of_perils_exit → 16 living_in_simulation → 17 person_affecting_view" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJy1WWtz2zYW%2FSt3PNtdybVlUm856844sdxm1kk8jrOdTpxRIBKSUJMEFyAtq2ny2%2FcAfIiK6QlTT794aBI499z3BfRpz%2BcLlgbJC%2BnzveO9oyM6OTmha8VERIkkT7E%2FNnhYR3STdh23T2upAv9O8DWt3Vl3NpgNZ6PZeOb2Zm5%2F5g5n7ohaOpExuaO2wbqJgHmqdRrGiZAReStAH5NDMVPSWwkWGGR30iWXFkzN2JptZqs0ZJEuPnSJRSJkgZ5pGfL1iiXFlwEt0iRVPN8wC1mScDVbi2Q184X2ZBolIloWy4cUyer72c7uYtWoFJfDsVkgS5Fj0uliwZXdLr1Uc79UoEeeDAIWaz7z%2BVIxn%2BtcRLmkT4kI%2BUwuZjEwIIPfixLbHVIg7gyyiGZahGnArM2KzyPCJi2jGQMDz2pgPGFNPGXeitjWzkITo8tNssLzQgSc4NDtZ31EibEj8319QIojCkTENUllwRQ%2FhHtYyKG%2B0HifrHjmuX9pmDzyLMYzqBvGUhsLlwuwN%2FI5EPFKaIumExb5LJARpxBhFnToYxlF07uPhqrZzu9jKIWNdyxIOcmFRdgGXMeCPec6oXm6odSIMRs1ryp2TG9XSoQx%2FcoDxBOnSyV%2FB262%2B%2Bfp6%2BnV6fX0jOYbWvKIK5bwTrwpopv78EbVTPv4eICwSTIyxpJAsljvIo%2BrxKgcSoUwLi2ms7WZOVgcB4LrDr3dhJ1ALiOpEFutT%2FHggOLJ4HPbYllvTZwf6MXLZ3blnCcsexsrOWdzEYgERObSqO2b1HzvHJD7oUPnzEskZELXDAoLYuODKDkgLYmbwJBqCc9N36%2FPTi9%2BO%2FrHB5rzQK6RcGav9TC%2Fx3OwwXZgw6oWC7L91EsyX8B7HGkC9ReBTLFrBcef5dlEJw8VRJZ3nLFV0zyOP7eJbHABEzqsuViugI2aoDizebqCtUwcampdy5BpcfuM%2FguFzLeu03VgrDL7LpUA9WRTL9ntuLngYWeQC%2Bb3iWIVsewO%2FjPQ0JlHCKMS%2B3HxWTpXtHYtdIyXhyaz6UfyWMJ0omQMi5kCEqVZFptEZOowLwhZkLeuWKj55ugtwiaiL84PRxtFd5peS%2BWvWKrpi9sZmJfPIOgEcUhF%2BQKXoticW8RXqOLCxJqqt0g3t8fAyc3xgAy8XJqEwRjqTtyxOUpHIQgI8I0IhU6EBz8qvEe1twtNCCLRlxESqn1MP8H8jALp3XL%2FEGmALIaBbS7fRFnpm6LyNSXdK0hrjwX8MI2LkCyLRq6JyF6v2B9MIcTgPIS5F0gT4mwBK1OYiWQRMkxtSPMkCXiIbKHWG%2BUjS6wbAZ%2BxfEY%2B96RSHLUYYrbLkTIR%2FoexQKjqc2TGrQnUsn6%2FkKbbpGBwUuZ2C%2FaZZCpdtiqlXqVoRCiVS6DLdLmihbRFzngr17FdFKvn0ogMEZpOD0ZVqIRRcsllHPBzxWyNrrdqjx86ozIvHWwvrLsyFbOIA3iuqlcWJMzzVGorvoSFjCxar1Bl7hEUaJwbtO9j%2BtLjrks5I%2FS0BT%2FccIYI