and x-risk work keeps its urgency but loses most of its astronomical multiplier. Mutually exclusive with the time-of-perils-exit reading. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 6 no_discounting_future_humans → 7 animals_matter_a_lot → 8 suffering_focused → 13 collapse_degrades_future → 15 space_expansion_backfires" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJylWX9z2zYS%2FSo7nuudlLNkkrJ%2B2efOOLHcZs5JM45zmU6cUSASklBTBA8grahp%2BtnvASAlKpLPTP1PRiGBt28fdhe79JeDiE9ZHmcvZMQPTg6Ojujs7IxuFBMJZZJCxX5f4ccyods88PxjWkoVR%2FeCL2npj4Nxd9wb98eDsd8Z%2B11q6Eym5HebBuU2Adq51vkizYRMKJwD9IQ8SpmS4Vyw2GD6w4B8mjI1Zku2Gs%2FzBUt0%2BSIglogFi%2FVYywVfzllWvunSNM9yxYsN4wXLMq7GS5HNx5HQocyTTCSzcnmPEll9Pt7aXa7qr80VcGwcy7XJAel8OuXKbpdhrnm0dqBDoYxjlmo%2BjvhMsYjrwsR6SZd0ykI%2B5p9TmIQg4wkL76ZCcW2VGrFwTmwjl9DE6M0qm%2BP3VMSccCKb1%2FqIMiMHiyJ9SIrjGEXCNUllwRRvQWW24PBCaDzP5twdwD80lEtCi3EK1otUaiPUegH2JhEHIh4JR01nLIlYLBNOC8RJ3KZP6zAY3X8yVM12eMbDDBvvWZxzklOLsImYtgV7znVGk3xFuTFjNmpedeyEzq%2BuLkcXbvVPo9ej6%2FOb0QVNVjTjCVcs4%2B10VYYjj0S2JcszvDzEaWfOuFEOSBbrXRJylRkXF1Ih%2BtYKabfWuc%2FSNBZct%2BntatGO5SyRCiHR%2BJJ2Dykddr82LZY9naH3A714eWpXTnjG3NNUyQmbiFhkIDKRxs3I5NIH75D8j226ZGEmYZMp7qCwIDWaJ9khaUncBIJUM5zU6MPy4vzq16O%2FfaQJj%2BUSeWL22hPln%2FE7XmE7sKGixYLtKA8zpz1OiyPU4P40ljl2zXHQF0US0Nmug0jOtjewbpqfg69NIhtMwIQPSy5mc2AjlRVnNr3mUMvEnabGjVwwLe5O6T9wyLwLvMCDWOukeaMEqGer%2FZb9tl8Y7rW7hWH%2BOVOsYpbd4%2FwMNHzmCcJmjf2weZeFFa99C53iYSsTC07%2FpJBlTGdKplDM5H2SM5uBJvGYahV57IK6cc0Wmq%2BO3iJsEvrT%2B%2BFopehe02upojnLNf3pt7vm4SkMnSEOqaw64FLWiEuL%2BAplV5hYU%2FsVCQo9ul4hxw4ZnPJaEgYx1L24ZxOUitIQEHA2YiF0JkKco8JzFGm70IQgEnuWIKGaJ%2FQj5GcUy%2FCORy2kAbIWAtvcxRmayvW8KFeP8UYMBesY6hXcMyUWRtCtOlE4s5yb8saZQjSvq6MpYUwtXGWZs9%2BZiqhxwfMo4StkRpSzuJXbyoGTkCI6kmoiMmS1SKbKHCfSAOCn9J4jQJVe4GbQhsHcppGCeFPYwAbN42nLRJIIBU9CZJRuFhXjAu4imziiLLQRWMnNFB4xtUJiJtxsxe9Dej66%2FOV65OqLRXDBiwOCuqY4LHCPJVkL90s4hwJr6ejtu1evzq9%2FdZmLwu6MQH%2Bch0WayIyH1DApTeevLxACSjBUNFcImm26gVDTHAfsikRrs