68% best&lt;br&gt;   runner-up Wild insects (humane pesticides) · 29%&lt;br&gt;(Nick Bostrom)" tooltip="&lt;b&gt;parochial + far_away_humans + animals_somewhat + future_humans_matter_with_discounting + no_discounting_future_humans + animals_matter_a_lot + suffering_focused + collapse_degrades_future + space_expansion_backfires + living_in_simulation&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;If most observers like us are simulated, the astronomical future that justified x-risk work probably gets switched off long before it happens. The same expected-value reasoning that bought astronomical stakes now attenuates them: future-facing value is multiplied by the probability the simulation keeps running, and the ranking slides back toward the present. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 6 no_discounting_future_humans → 7 animals_matter_a_lot → 8 suffering_focused → 13 collapse_degrades_future → 15 space_expansion_backfires → 16 living_in_simulation" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJylWWtv2zgW%2FSsXwc6u3U0cyY5fyWaAtHFmik07RZpuMWgKl5ZoixtJ1JJSXE%2Bn89v3kHpYrh1Erb8EikSee%2B6T99JfDnw%2BZ1mYvpA%2BPzg9OD6m8%2FNzulVMxJRK8hT7Y4WHZUx3WddxT2gpVeg%2FCL6kpTvtTvvTwXQ4HU3d3tTtT90BtXQqE3IHbQN0FwPwQussSlIhY%2FIC4J6SQwlT0gsECw2sO%2B6SS3OmpmzJVtMgi1isyw9dYrGIWKinWkZ8GbC0%2FNKneZZmihcbphFLU66mS5EGU19oT2ZxKuJFuXxAsay%2Fn27sLlcNK3EFHJuGshI5Ip3N51zZ7dLLNPcrBXrkyTBkieZTny8U87kuRFRL%2BqQT5vEp%2F5xAJAwynTHvfi4Ur%2BTDgqF4MPginmoRZSEzlrOGnDAvILa2ptDE6M0qDfA8FyEn%2BGz9WR9TaqzFfF8fkuJwtIghSCoLpvgRnMAiDiWFxvs04Ll%2F%2FqFh2NizGGdQKkqkNnasFmBv7HMg4pXQFk2nLPZZKGNOESIp7NCnKlAmD58MVbMdinMvxcYHFmac5NwirGOqY8Gec53SLFtRZsSYjZrXFTult4ESUULveYio4fRGyf8CN9%2F9y%2BT15ObidnJJsxUteMwVS3knWZUBzH2RbpjpGT4eIjjSnIyxJJAs1rvY4yo1KkdSIVgri%2Bl8bW4OliSh4LpDb1dRJ5SLWCpEUOtL0j%2BkZNz%2F2rZY1ltj5yd68fLMrpzxlOVvEyVnbCZCkYLITBq1fZN9H5xDcj926Ip5qYRM6JpDYUFifBCnh6QlcRMYUi3gucmH5eXF9e%2FHf%2FtIMx7KJdLK7LUe5p%2FxHK6wHdiwqsWCbD%2Fz0twX8B5HZEL9eSgz7Arg%