ives saved from extinction — loses almost all its force. Only the harm to people who exist regardless still counts. This is the standard premise longtermism&#x27;s critics deny (discussed as the key objection in Greaves &amp; MacAskill&#x27;s &#x27;The Case for Strong Longtermism&#x27;). It requires no_discounting_future_humans, the astronomical-stakes move it pushes back on. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 6 no_discounting_future_humans → 7 animals_matter_a_lot → 8 suffering_focused → 13 collapse_degrades_future → 16 living_in_simulation → 17 person_affecting_view" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJylWWtv2zgW%2FSsXwc6u3UkcyY5f6WaAtHFmik07QZpuMWgKl5ZomxtJ1JJSHG%2Bn%2Fe17SD0s1wqqjr8UrkSee%2B65D14qnw98PmdpkLyUPj84PTg%2BprOzM7pVTESUSPIU%2B98aP1YR3aVdxz2hlVSB%2FyD4ilbutDvtTwfT4XQ0dXtTdzB1h9TSiYzJHbYN0F0EwHOt0zBOhIzIWwL3lByKmZLeUrDAwLrjLrk0Z2rKVmw9XaYhi3TxokssEiEL9FTLkK%2BWLCne9GmeJqni%2BYZpyJKEq%2BlKJMupL7Qn0ygR0aJYPqBIVp9Pt3YXq4aluRyOTQNZmhyRTudzrux26aWa%2B6UDPfJkELBY86nPF4r5XOcmyiUDCsSD2SuiqRZhGjCrSvF6SDFXWkZTBhue5WiEtiJOmLcktlFSaGJ0vU6W%2BD0XASfEa%2FNaH1NilGK%2Brw9JcQRZRFyTVBZM8SMEgIUcDgqN58mSZ7H5h4aokWcxnsOhMJbaaFguwN7I50DEI6Etmk5Y5LNARpxCZFHQoU9lkkwePhmqZjt%2FjOEUNj6wIOUk5xZhk08dC%2FaC64Rm6ZpSY8Zs1Lzq2Cm9XSoRxvSeB8gYTtdK%2Fge42e5fJ28mN%2Be3kwuarWnBI65Ywjvxukhe7otkS6ZneHmIxEgyMkZJIFmsd5HHVWJcDqVCopaK6WxtJgeL40Bw3aG367ATyEUkFbKn9TnuH1I87n9pWywbrbHzE7189dyunPGEZU9jJWdsJgKRgMhMGrd9U3kfnENyP3boknmJhE34mkFhQWxiECWHpCVxkxhSLRC5yYfVxfnVH8d%2F%2B0gzHsgVSsrstRHmj%2FgdrLEd2FDVYsG2n3pJFgtEj6MQ4P48kCl2LRH4i7xe6GzXQdRxxxlZN83P0Zc2kU0uYMKHFReLJbBR9YozW4lLqGXyUFPrVoZMi%2Fvn9G84ZN51na4Dscr6ulYC1JN1vWW34%2BaGB51%2Bbpg%2FJopVzLIHxM9Aw2ceIY1K7KfNZwVb8dq10DEeHiUi5PQzeSxhOlEyhmKmRURpVsWmEJk6yks%2BS%2FLWDQs1Xx%2B%2FRdpE9NX56Xit6EHTG6n8JUs1fXU7ffPwOQydIQ%2BpaFDgUrSTS4v4Gk1amFxT9Yp0cz36Ti7HDhlEuZSEQQz1IB7YDK2jMAQExEaEQifCQxwVnqOf24UmBVHoiwgF1T6lXyA%2Fo0B699w%2FQhmgiiGwrWXEsGxtL6VptSny76xM%2Bx